    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ Ego<persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/3042"> Secundus
                            Robertus</persName> Dei gratia Capuanorum <rs key="#Princeps"
                            >princeps</rs> promitto, et per haec sancta Dei evangelia juro tibi
                        domno <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4227">Segnoricto</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84"
                            >Cassinensis</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">Monasterii</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">Abbati</rs>, quod ab hac hora et deinceps non ero in
                        consilio, vel in facto, seu consensu, ut vitam, vel quodlibet membrum tui
                        corporis perdas, aut captus sis mala captione ad tuum dapnum honorem, et
                        terras, quas Cassinense monasterium S. Benedicti tenet, et dominatur, vel
                        quod in antea recuperaverit per se, vel per suos homines, vel in antea meo
                        consiglio infra principatum Capuanum accquisierit, et quae tempore <persName
                            key="#Princeps #greatGrandparentOf" ref="#people/3001"
                            >Richardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>
                        <rs key="#greatGrandparentOf">proavi</rs> mei, et <persName
                            key="#Princeps #grandparentOf" ref="#people/3002">Jordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>
                        <rs key="#grandparentOf">avi</rs>, et <persName
                            key="#Princeps #uncle/auntOf" ref="#people/3010">Richardi</persName>, et
                            <persName key="#Princeps #uncle/auntOf" ref="#people/3019"
                            >Robberti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principum</rs>
                        <rs key="#uncle/auntOf">patruorum</rs> meorum, et <persName
                            key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3022">Jordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs> mei praedicto Cassinensi monasterio, vel in
                        suis subditis <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiis</rs> offertum vel datum est
                        usque nunc, et nominatim <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3061">Sanctae Agatae</orgName> sitam prope <rs
                            key="#Walls">muros</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Walls" ref="#places/4000">Aversae</placeName> cum
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                            >hominibus</rs> qualiter Jordanus princeps avus meus eidem monasterio
                        dedit, et concessit, et <rs key="#Castle">oppidum</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Castle"
                            ref="#places/4537">Pontiscurbi</placeName> cum suis pertinentiis,
                        qualiter Richardus princeps patruus meus illud concessit, et confirmavit
                        praedicto monasterio, et domno <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4222"
                            >Hoderisio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">Abbati</rs> adjuvabo te, et praedictum monasterium tenere,
                        ac defendere contra omnes homines, qui tibi illud aut inde auferre
                        temptaverit si inde summonitus fuero, nisi tale exonium intervenerit, quod
                        propter hoc non sit inventum, et transacto exonio infra quadraginta dies
                        predicta aut adimplebo, aut rectum, vel gratam concordiam tibi inde fieri
                        faciam; et facto recto vel grata concordia, in hoc Sacramento permanebo. Hac
                        omnia praedicta observabo per bonam fidem, absque fraude, et malo ingenio,
                        quod sit ad praedicti monasterii, aut tui damnum pertineat. Hoc factum est
                        in <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capuana</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> die Dominico, quarto die stante mense
                        Februarii in anno Dominicae incarnationis millesimo centesimo vigesimo
                        octavo, per indictionem sextam ante praesencia subscriptorum <rs
                            key="#Witness">testium</rs> videlicet. <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/4226">Ri. de Caleno</persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/3040">Ugo de Labolita</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3035"
                            >Odoal.</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">Camerarii</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/4287">Philippi de Surrento</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Turstainus de Rivo Matricio">Tostayni de Rivo
                                Matricio</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ro. de Aczia">Ro. de Aczia</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Bertram">Borteraymi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes de Calatia">Joannis de
                                Calatia</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Iulianus de Juttura">Juliani de Juttura</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Raginaldus de Guelcu">Raynaldi de
                                Guelcu</name></persName>. </ab>
                </div>
